  "title": "Service Technician",
  "description": "<p>Job Requirements:</p>\n<p>- Must possess driving licence, class 3</p>\n<p>- Must be physically fit</p>\n<p>- Must be customer service oriented</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Responsibilities:</p>\n<p>1. Carries out minor repairs through the provision of after sales servicing for end-users (Indoor and Outdoor Servicing)</p>\n<p>2. Gives feedback received from end-user to management to enhance product quality and service.</p>\n<p>3. Liaises with the Service Manager in handling customer complaints and the servicing of customers’ heaters</p>\n<p>4. Responsible for giving customers satisfaction in line with our Company Quality Policy of Total Customer Satisfaction</p>\n<p>5. Work harmoniously with both the internal customer (i.e. the Customer Service Officer) and the external customer (i.e. the end-user).</p>\n<p>6. Reports any non- conformance matters to the Service Manager</p>\n<p>7. Any other assignments as directed by the Service Manager</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
